            <title>[LU-1700] Test failure on test suite parallel-scale-nfsv4, subtest test_iorfpp</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1700</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/910f5a10-d2d5-11e1-8823-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/910f5a10-d2d5-11e1-8823-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_iorfpp failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ior failed! 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From client-2 testlog&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;+ su mpiuser sh -c &quot;/usr/lib64/openmpi/1.4-gcc/bin/mpirun -mca boot ssh  -mca btl tcp,self -np 4 -machinefile /tmp/parallel-scale-nfs.machines /usr/bin/IOR -a POSIX -b 1g -o /mnt/lustre/d0.ior.fpp/iorData -t 2m -v -w -r -i 1 -T 30 -k -F &quot;
Permission denied.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
